#
#   mountssh - mount + ssh any remote
#   Usage: mountssh [FLAGS] [PROFILE]
#   Daily chores:
#       mountssh nas        -> mount + drop into shell
#       mountssh -m termux  -> only mount phone locally
#       mountssh -s pi      -> only ssh into pi
